query.result:
70 I am Beatrice who makes you go;
71 I come from the place where I long to return;
72 love moved me, which makes me speak.

79 your command pleases me so much
80 that to obey it, if it were already possible, would be too late for me;
81 there is nothing more you need to do than reveal your wish to me.

88 One should only fear those things
89 that have the power to harm others;
90 not the others, for they are not fearsome.
